net.wombatrpgs.mgne.data
Class Database

java.lang.Object
  net.wombatrpgs.mgne.data.Database

public class Database
extends java.lang.Object

I'm not really sure if this should be an interface, but the way I see it, this should just be the *best* database because all databases should have the same use cases and the same underlying good methods. But yeah, the idea is that you ask this class to do get all the schema of type x or named x or whatever the hell.
